Jalaine ir'Thavar is the granddaughter of [[Traven ir'Thavar]]. Her father Taraval spend the Thavar family's wealth in establishing the ward of [[Dannel's Pride]] in [[Stormreach]] for the people of [[Cyre]], and today Jalaine shares her family's home with two dozen refugees. Even though she is no longer wealthy, she shares her grandfather's love of Cyre and is always searching for peaceful solutions to the problems of the refugees.